CRUSE

Cycle Route Uptake & Scenario Estimation

About

Transport Infrastructure Ireland commissioned ITS Leeds and AECOM to develop the Cycle Route Uptake and Scenario Estimation (CRUSE) tool to support strategic cycle network planning and investment prioritisation across the Republic of Ireland. The CRUSE tool has been used to develop a number of scenarios for cycle network investment in the Republic of Ireland. CRUSE estimates the potential uptake of a cycle route based on factors such as distance, terrain, and attractiveness. This information can be used to inform decisions about where best to invest in new or improved cycle routes.
